text: We Born, We grow, We reach adolescence/adult, We get Older, Lastly We gain Elder. Within all these ages (life span), we get stress, we get pain, we get fear, we fight, we lost our family & friends, we fight for life again, we fight for health recovery again and again and again repeatedly. Finally we say Goodbye for our families, friends & the world at all without seeing our hope, met our plan get sufficient pleasures & satisfaction, without seeing our country prosperous enough to feed our generation & upsetting being too poor we have no confidence even the our future generation get Peace, Love, Respect/Dignity, Empathy, Satisfaction/pleasure of life, Destiny etc. This is called our "Life-Cycle" we never understand this. Hence, this song is dedicated for this Life; the song name is "Memory" or "Tizita". But how many Memories (Tizitas) do we have in life starting from childhood-Adult-Older-Elder ages. The memories we have possessed were categorized in to two 'Bad-Memories' & the 'Good-memories".
